LoadSkin Plugin for DokuWiki (2026) for PHP 8.1

Fork created so that plugin works with PHP 8.1 without showing visible errors to the user. (Previous one has not been updated since 2017.)
I will maintain it if anything breaks on my DokuWiki instance, but have no plans for new features as it appears to do exactly what I want it to.

All documentation for the LoadSkin Plugin is available online at:

  * http://dokuwiki.org/plugin:loadskin

